Python-Premailer
================

Python-Premailer transforms standard HTML into a format best suited for e-mail
delivery by creating inline CSS styles.


Documentation
-------------

Extensive documentation and installation instructions can be found in the
``docs`` directory of this source distribution.


Dependencies
------------

Python 2.5+ - http://www.python.org/
python-lxml - http://pypi.python.org/pypi/lxml
python-cssutils - http://pypi.python.org/pypi/cssutils


Support
-------

For any feature requests or issues regarding this project, please e-mail
rcoyner@gmail.com.
